This cabinet card is a reprint of an older CdV of Amos Hanks II.
I figured this out because until 1876 Grand Ave in Milwaukee was known as Spring Street.
So based on the address in the studio mark it couldn't have been printed before Amos's death in 1866.
Then I found the original CDV in another album which confirmed it.
